        return ["Public and Micro Finance", "Child Development and Women's Affairs", "Community Support", "Housing and Construction", "Labour Welfare and Regulation", "Transportation", "Justice System", "Foreign Affairs", "Public Administration", "Healthcare", "National Security", "Urban Development"]
